### to measure metrics by endpoint
## https://github.com/kenshoo/metrics-play
GET     /talachitas/admin/metrics                          com.kenshoo.play.metrics.MetricsController.metrics

# Home page
GET       /talachitas/noqueue/v1/users                       controllers.ClientController.listUsers
POST      /talachitas/noqueue/v1/users                       controllers.ClientController.addUser
OPTIONS   /talachitas/noqueue/v1/users                       controllers.OptionsController.options

DELETE    /talachitas/noqueue/v1/users/:id                   controllers.ClientController.deleteUser(id : Long)
GET       /talachitas/noqueue/v1/users/:id                   controllers.ClientController.retrieveUser(id: Long)
PATCH     /talachitas/noqueue/v1/users/:id                   controllers.ClientController.patchUser(id: Long)
OPTIONS   /talachitas/noqueue/v1/users/:id                   controllers.OptionsController.optionsLong(id: Long)

